Whitmore has part of the plan.

01:36:08.330 --> 01:36:11.299
- Don't believe him.
- Whitmore is a government agent.

01:36:11.333 --> 01:36:13.135
She'll never believe you.

01:36:13.168 --> 01:36:15.137
The design was just bent, Nikki.

01:36:15.170 --> 01:36:18.273
