about everything!

01:36:27.749 --> 01:36:28.783
- Go!
- No

01:36:28.817 --> 01:36:29.784
- Move!
- Go!

01:36:29.818 --> 01:36:31.086
-Go!

01:36:31.119 --> 01:36:33.155
You can't get in the way too.

01:36:33.188 --> 01:36:34.489
-Charlie!

01:36:42.831 --> 01:36:43.866
Come on!

01:36:59.948 --> 01:37:01.283
You need a doctor.

01:37:01.316 --> 01:37:03.518
You gotta get out of here.
And don't look back.

01:37:03.551 --> 01:37:04.987
Just rest.

01:37:05.020 --> 01:37:08.123
You drew the half
you'd never seen.

01:37:08.156 --> 01:37:10.225
Lot of people
want a piece of you.

01:37:11.126 --> 01:37:13.161
Well, they have
a pattern of you.

01:37:14.162 --> 01:37:15.730
There's a joker in every deck.

01:37:19.234 --> 01:37:23.238
Well, actually, there's two.

01:37:50.732 --> 01:37:51.833
Where is it?

01:37:53.668 --> 01:37:54.937
She burned it.

01:37:56.905 --> 01:37:59.307
That would be a great loss.

01:38:02.710 --> 01:38:03.811
If it were true.

